<h2 class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">If the requirement to cooperate 
 <span style="font-style: italic;">changes</span> after a TA/MA referral 
 to the CSEU</h2>
<p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers" style="color: #ff0000; font-size: 14pt; 
	 font-weight: bold;">SNIPPET</p>
<p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">In a TA case, if a customer:</p>
<ul style="list-style: disc;">
	<li><p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">checks only Box 2 in Section 
	 C of the <span class="Notices_name"><a title="Application Form" href="http://otda.state.nyenet/assets/pages/HTML/Child_Support_Application-Referral.htm" 
											 target="_blank">LDSS-4882</a>,</span></p></li>
</ul>
<p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers" style="margin-left: 67px;"><span 
	 class="Notices_name" style="color: #000000;">AND</span></p>
<ul style="list-style: disc;">
	<li><p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">is subsequently found 
	 ineligible for TA or MA, </p></li>
</ul>
<p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers" style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; 
	 margin-left: 67px;">AND</p>
<ul style="list-style: disc;">
	<li><p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">the customer stills seeks 
	 child support services,</p></li>
</ul>
<p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">an application for such services 
 must be made pursuant to <span class="Legislation_Titles">SSL § 111-g</span>. 
 &#160;</p>
<p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">However, if the TA or MA case 
 was closed less than 30 days prior, rather than filling out a new <span 
	 class="Notices_name"><a title="Application Form" href="http://otda.state.nyenet/assets/pages/HTML/Child_Support_Application-Referral.htm" 
							 target="_blank">LDSS-4882</a></span>, the 
 applicant may revise the previously submitted <span class="Notices_name"><a 
	 title="Application Form" href="http://otda.state.nyenet/assets/pages/HTML/Child_Support_Application-Referral.htm" 
	 target="_blank">LDSS-4882</a>.</span></p>
<p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers" style="margin-left: 67px; text-decoration: underline; ">To 
 do this, the applicant must:</p>
<ol style="list-style: decimal;">
	<ol style="list-style: decimal;">
		<ol style="list-style: decimal;">
			<li class="Numbered_List_-_Numbers"><p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">Check 
			 Box 1 in <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;">Section 
			 C – Application/Affirmation for Child Support Services;</span></p></li>
			<li class="Numbered_List_-_Numbers"><p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">Complete 
			 the associated signature area; and </p></li>
			<li class="Numbered_List_-_Numbers"><p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">Initial 
			 the changes to mark the <span class="Notices_name"><a title="Application Form" 
			 href="http://otda.state.nyenet/assets/pages/HTML/Child_Support_Application-Referral.htm" 
			 target="_blank">LDSS-4882</a></span> as having been amended</p></li>
		</ol>
	</ol>
</ol>
<p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">(Note that the worker should have 
 asked the TA referral customer during the original intake interview whether 
 he/she wants to pursue child support services even in the event of denial 
 of temporary assistance. If so, the customer should have checked off and 
 signed both Box 1 and Box 2 in Section C of the LDSS-4882.)</p>
<p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers" style="background-color: #ffff00;">??MT 
 - Below is language from ADM:</p>
<p class="Normal_Pre-Bullet_Pre-Numbers">If an individual reapplies for 
 TA or MA more than thirty (30) days after the TA or MA case that was originally 
 referred to the CSEU has been closed, a new <span class="Notices_name"><a 
	 title="Application Form" href="http://otda.state.nyenet/assets/pages/HTML/Child_Support_Application-Referral.htm" 
	 target="_blank">LDSS-4882</a></span> form must be submitted to the 
 CSEU. &#160;</p>
