 - re the above sentence (from an ADM): It talks about 30 days after &#160;the 
 TA or MA case is closed...but it seems that in this instance, the TA or 
 MA would have been DENIED (i.e. ineligible), and a case would never have 
 been built. Correct? How is CSEU notified of &quot;closure&quot; of the 
 TA or MA case?</p>
